headline: AT&T Opens New Regional Hub in Chantilly Marking Major Investment in Fairfax County
summary: Fairfax County, Virginia--(Newsfile Corp. - August 13, 2025) - Last week, AT&T marked a significant milestone with the official ribbon-cutting ceremony for its new regional hub in the Chantilly-area of Fairfax County.
